{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/git/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"tableOfContents":"","html":"<ul>\n<li>파일을 트래킹하지 않는 명령어<br>\n<code class=\"language-jstext\">git update-index --assume-unchanged [file]</code></li>\n<li>pushed commit을 없애고 새로 커밋\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">git reset [recoverCommitId]</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">git add .</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">git commit</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-jstext\">git push --force</code></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Git 명령어","date":"November 04, 2020","spoiler":"잘 외워지지 않는 명령어"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/git/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}